## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **imatinib Gleevec 2001** = first FDA targeted cancer therapy. BCR-ABL kinase ATP-pocket inhibitor. CML 임상 paradigm shift — historical IFN-α + hydroxyurea + allo-HSCT 시대 종료. quantum-VQE 의 ATP pocket benchmark.
2. **asciminib Scemblix 2021** = first FDA allosteric STAMP (Specifically Targeting the ABL Myristoyl Pocket). ATP-competitive 4+ 세대 후 next mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 allosteric pocket leverage 직접 fit.
3. **ponatinib Iclusig 2012** = first FDA T315I-active pan-BCR-ABL TKI. T315I gatekeeper mutation 임상 unmet need. cardiovascular black-box 부작용 trade-off — 만성 long-term safety open.
4. **dasatinib + nilotinib + bosutinib 2006-2012** = second/third/fourth-gen BCR-ABL TKI 임상 paradigm. imatinib resistance + intolerance line option. selectivity vs off-target Src + KIT trade-off.
5. **omacetaxine Synribo 2012** = 만성 protein synthesis inhibitor (eEF1A) — T315I refractory niche. quantum-VQE 의 ribosomal A-site interface 한정.
6. **TFR (treatment-free remission) paradigm 2010s+** = DMR (deep molecular response — MR4 / MR4.5 / MR5) 후 TKI 중단 가능. CML 임상 cure-like paradigm. 양자-VQE 의 long-term molecular response prediction 한정.
7. **K-CML 산정특례 framework** = imatinib + dasatinib + nilotinib + bosutinib + ponatinib + asciminib K-domestic + generic + biosimilar (cross-K_pharma_industry). K-임상 cost framework cross-link.
8. **pediatric CML rare** = 만성 청소년 + 영유아 + pediatric CML — adult CML 1% 미만. dasatinib + imatinib pediatric label expansion. quantum-VQE 의 pediatric dosing 한정.
9. **allo-HSCT historical 1L → second/third-line** = TKI era 후 allo-HSCT 가 BP-CML + multi-TKI failure 한정. CML cure 가능 historical 유일 option 였음.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, CML 임상 의미 한정.

